-- Dr. Brendan Reilly Says Everyone Needs `One Doctor' (Audio)
-- B y
-- 2013-10-21T12:04:15Z
-- http://www.bloomberg.com/news/2013-10-21/dr-brendan-reilly-says-everyone-needs-one-doctor-audio-.html
Dr. Brendan Reilly, physician and 
author discusses his book "One Doctor: Close Calls, Cold Cases 
and the Mysteries of Medicine," and says people should have 
either a primary care doctor or specialist who knows them well 
and takes care of their medical needs. Reilly talked with 
Bloomberg's Pimm Fox and  Carol Massar  on Bloomberg Radio's 
"Taking Stock" on October 18th.    (Source: Bloomberg)  Running time 11:02
 